# ── Local-only working artifacts — repo is CODE-ONLY (no images/exports ever) ──
# Root-scoped (/*) on purpose: ignores the loose screenshots/exports that pile up at the
# repo root WITHOUT reaching into subdirs (e.g. audit/) that other tooling may own. The only
# intentional image is the base64-inline logo, so "no committed root images" is the invariant.
/*.png
/*.docx
